      "content": "i lost everything. the company is gone, the liquidators are calling every hour, and the debt is... i dont even know how to describe it. it's more than i can ever pay back. i just keep thinking about my family seeing me like this. the shame is actually physical. i can't face them. i can't face anyone. it feels like there's no version of the future where i'm not a complete disgrace.",
